    rdfs:comment 'Type of government procurement mechanism used for this contract. IDIQ = Indefinite Delivery Indefinite Quantity, BPA = Blanket Purchase Agreement, CCS = Crown Commercial Service. [ENUM-REF-CANDIDATE: GSA Schedule|IDIQ|BPA|G-Cloud|CCS Framework|State Contract|Cooperative Purchase|Direct Award — 8 candidates stripped; promote to reference product]' ;
